ur]]\n|[[Kanchipuram]],<br> [[Kanchipuram district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|12.840653| 79.703250}}\n|[[File:Kanchipuram.in Kamakshi-Amman Temple - panoramio.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Anjilai Valli sametha Sri Adi Varaha Perumal\n|\n|-\n|55\n|[[Tiru pavla vannam|Thiruppavalavannam]]\n|[[Kanchipuram]],<br> [[Kanchipuram district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|12.843658| 79.707604}}\n|[[File:Manavalamamunigal 05.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Pavalavalli sametha Sri Pavalavarna Perumal\n|\n|-\n|56\n|[[Tiru parameswara vinnagaram|Thiru Parameswara Vinnagaram]]\n|[[Kanchipuram]],<br> [[Kanchipuram district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|12.837151| 79.709482}}\n|[[File:Parameswara Vinnagaram.JPG|130px|center]] \n|Sri Vaikundavalli sametha Sri Vaikundanatha Perumal\n|\n|-\n|57\n|[[Vijayaraghava Perumal temple|Thiruputkuzhi]]\n|[[Thiruputkuzhi]],<br> [[Kanchipuram district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|12.872642| 79.618683}}\n|[[File:Tirupukuzhi1.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Maragadhavalli sametha Sri Vijayaraghava Perumal\n|\n|-\n|58\n|[[Bhaktavatsala Perumal Temple, Thirunindravur|Thirunindravur]]\n|[[Thiruninravur|Thirunindravur]],<br> [[Tiruvallur District]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|13.112501| 80.026096}}\n|[[File:Bakthavtsala perumal gopuram.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Sudhavalli sametha Sri Bhaktavatsala Perumal\n|\n|-\n|59\n|[[Veeraraghava Swami Temple (Thiruevvul)|Thiruvallur]]\n|[[Thiruvallur]],<br> [[Tiruvallur district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|13.143204| 79.907439}}\n|[[File:Tiruvallur9.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Kanakavalli sametha Sri Vaidya Veeraraghava Perumal\n|\n|-\n|60\n|[[Parthasarathy Kovil|Thiruvallikeni]]\n|[[Chennai]],<br> [[Chennai district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|13.053920| 80.276942}}\n|[[File:Tiruvallikeni1.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Rukmini sametha Sri Venkatakrishna Perumal\n|\n|-\n|61\n|[[Ranganatha Temple, Thiruneermalai|Thiruneermalai]]\n|[[Kanchipuram]],<br> [[Kanchipuram district]], <br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|12.963808| 80.114953}}\n|[[File:Th