jayasana Perumal\n|\n|-\n|93\n|[[ThiruPulingudi Perumal Temple|Thiruppuliangudi]]\n|Thirupulingudi,<br>[[Thoothukudi district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.60972| 77.976037}}\n|[[File:Thirupuliyangudi3.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Malar magal Naachiyaar and Sri Poomagal Naachiyaar sametha Sri Kaaichina Vendhan Perumal\n|\n|-\n|94\n|[[Irattai Thiruppathy|Thirutholaivillimangalam (Navathirupathi)]]\n|Tholavillimangalam,<br>[[Thoothukudi district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.60972| 77.97603}}\n|[[File:Aravinda Lochanar temple2.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Karunthadanganni Naachiyaar sametha Sri Aravindalochana Perumal\n|\n|-\n|95\n|[[Sri Srinivasa Perumal Temple, Tirukulandhai|Thirukkulandai (Navathirupathi)]]\n|[[Perungulam]],<br>[[Thoothukudi district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.606968| 77.950545}}\n|[[File:Thirukulandhai1.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Alamelumangai thaayar and Sri Kulandhai Valli sametha Sri Srinivasa Perumal\n|\n|-\n|96\n|[[Vaithamanidhi Perumal Temple|Thirukkolur (Navathirupathi)]]\n|Thirukolur,<br>[[Thoothukudi district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.6065018| 77.97389}}\n|[[File:Thirukkolur3.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Amudhavalli and Sri Koloorvalli sametha Sri Vaitha Maanitha Perumal\n|\n|-\n|97\n|[[Makara Nedunkuzhai Kannan Temple|Thirupperai]]\n|[[Thenthiruperai]],<br>[[Thoothukudi district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.60650| 77.97389}}\n|[[File:Then Thirupperai3.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Kuzhaikkaadhu Valli, and Sri Thirupperai Naachiyaar sametha Sri Magara NedungKuzhai Kaathar Perumal\n|\n|-\n|98\n|[[AlwarThirunagari Temple|Thirukkurugur]]\n|[[Alwarthirunagari]],<br>[[Thoothukudi district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.60696| 77.95054}}\n|[[File:Azhwar Thirunagari9.jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Aadhinadha Valli and Sri Gurukoor valli sametha Sri Aadhinatha Perumal\n|\n|-\n|99\n|[[Srivilliputhur Andal Temple|Thiruvillipputhur]]\n|[[Srivilliputhur]],<br>[[Virudhunagar district]],<br>[[Tamil Nadu]]{{coord|8.60696| 77.95054}}\n|[[File:Andal Temple.jpg|130px|