 Kadal Magal sametha Sri Parkadal Natha Perumal\n|This Divya Desam is not located on Earth, but in the spiritual realm. \n|-\n|108\n|[[Vaikunta|Thirupparamapadham]]\n| Vinnulaga Tirupati\n|[[File:Brooklyn Museum - A Vision of Vishnu (Vaikuntha Darshana).jpg|130px|center]] \n|Sri Paramapada Nayaki sametha Sri Paramapadha Nathan\n|This Divya Desam is not located on Earth, but in the spiritual realm.\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Mangalasasanam by Divyadesam]]\n\n==Maps==\n* [http://maps.google.co.in/maps/ms?hl=en&gl=in&ptab=2&ie=UTF8&oe=UTF8&msa=0&msid=207842118129647355016.00043d9afbe3f59246002 Map of 108 Divyadesam along with links for virtual tour and travel information]\n* [https://maps.google.com/maps?q=divya+desam+around+trichy&hl=en&ll=10.833306,78.836517&spn=0.655521,1.229095&sll=10.826562,78.688889&sspn=0.344629,0.614548&z=10 Map of Divyadesam around Trichy]\n* [https://maps.google.com/maps?q=divyadesam+around+madurai&hl=en&ll=9.912038,78.11554&spn=1.382515,2.458191&sll=12.425848,86.000977&sspn=21.801911,39.331055&z=9 Map of Divyadesam around Madurai]\n* [http://maps.google.co.in/maps/ms?msa=0&msid=207842118129647355016.0004a43c4f36c55debcfc Map of Kerala Divyadesams]\n* [http://maps.google.co.in/maps/ms?msa=0&msid=207842118129647355016.0004718d879e1cb210590 Map of Ahobilam Divyadesam along with links photos]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==References==\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book|title=History of People and Their Environs|url=https://books.google.com/?id=crxUQR_qBXYC&pg=PA47&dq=poygai#v=onepage&q=poygai&f=false|publisher=Bharathi Puthakalayam|year=2011|last1=B. S.|first1=Chandrababu|last2=S.|first2=Ganeshram|last3=C.|first3=Bhavani|isbn=9789380325910|ref=B.S.}}\n* {{cite book|title=Philosophy and Theistic Mysticism of the \u0100l\u0332v\u0101rs|first= S. M. Srinivasa|last= Chari|publisher=Motilal Banarsidass Publishers|year=1997|isbn=9788120813427|url=https://books.google.com/?id=8TwHhuZrZ-wC&pg=PA16&dq=poygai#v=onepage&q=poygai&f=false|ref=Chari}}\n* {{cite 